{"tid":697292,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"你班廢老真係好煩 根本今輯美女廚房就好好笑！","createTime":"2018-06-11T01:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T09:54:59.000Z","uid":5652,"like":6,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"94983ab1fc768f7fa7bbe2e96dfb97f57ffdc4a2","tid":697292,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:00:23.000Z","msg":"成日係到講上輯方力申鄭中基梁漢文<br />\n除左梁丙，個2個主拎根本唔識尊重人！ 尢其方力申個死咸蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今輯主拎公平好多 又加左好多搞笑元素（估人！）<br />\nBob主持大局不嬲唔差<br />\n蕭正南冇方力申咁嘔心<br />\n張振朗靚仔過梁丙<br />\n<br />\n利申我今集睇到標眼水 但班廢老就日嘈夜嘈 懶係懷舊好威咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d216b522be597a9bfb1a819ff126652779629ccf","tid":697292,"uid":370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:02:39.000Z","msg":"Bob就係自以為自己好搞笑好識搞氣氛<br />\n無論係咩節目都好<br />\n其實佢講d野好撚廢 把聲好撚嘈 懶係激動咁做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79f5913228281e5edea576cbe8d4ef606d54598","tid":697292,"uid":5652,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"d216b522be597a9bfb1a819ff126652779629ccf","tid":697292,"uid":370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:02:39.000Z","msg":"Bob就係自以為自己好搞笑好識搞氣氛<br />\n無論係咩節目都好<br />\n其實佢講d野好撚廢 把聲好撚嘈 懶係激動咁做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:18:49.000Z","msg":"Bob係幾搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f094ae50cfb714db3c252cd20c21f0ee2de675","tid":697292,"uid":169761,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:18:06.000Z","msg":"蕭公子好有綜藝感，係應該拍多啲綜藝節目"},{"pid":"9dbea221e7f0a05eb04520cf83df310b06b2c1e2","tid":697292,"uid":61529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T05:15:07.000Z","msg":"呢集根本係特登嘥嘢食唔係煮嘢食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1ad23a67bce1fd4ea701ecd6092daa2